WEBVTT

1
00:41:34.750 --> 00:41:38.170 
奥克斯信中的谜语一点道理都没有
This riddle in Oxley's letter doesn't make any sense.

2
00:41:38.260 --> 00:41:41.000 
"跟随只有上帝才能看见的线"
"Follow the lines that only the gods can read "

3
00:41:41.000 --> 00:41:43.930 
"它会引领你到尤里奥纳的摇篮"
" that lead to Orellana's cradle. "

4
00:41:44.010 --> 00:41:46.300 
摇篮  他的出生地
Cradle, cradle, birth.

5
00:41:46.390 --> 00:41:49.390 
尤里奥纳不是生于秘鲁  而是在西班牙
Orellana wasn't born in Peru. He was born in Spain.

6
00:41:49.480 --> 00:41:51.390 
他是探险者  来这儿是为了黄金
He was a conquistador. He came here for the gold.

7
00:41:51.480 --> 00:41:52.890 
他后来怎么了？
What happened to him?

8
00:41:52.980 --> 00:41:57.230 
他和其它六名队员  活不见人死不见尸
He disappeared along with six others. Their bodies were never found.

